      <div class="container__large">
        <div class="badge__title--container">
            <p class="container__small badge__title--brief" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000" data-aos-delay="150">Have you ever wondered where the voice of Siri, Alexa or Google Assistant comes from? If you’ve ever asked: “Hey Google, what’s the weather forecast tomorrow?” you’ll be given the answer from a friendly digital helper, known as a chatbot.</p>
          <p class="container__small badge__title--brief" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000" data-aos-delay="250">
          A chatbot is a software system which uses conversational artificial intelligence (AI) technology to simulate a chat with you – the user. Aside from telling us the weather forecast, chatbots can help us in many areas of our lives at home, school or work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
